}}'''中国美国商会'''（The American Chamber of Commerce in the People's Republic of China，簡稱AmCham China）是一个[[非營利組織|非营利性]]的[[非政府组织|非政府组织]]，其成员包括来自在中国經營的900家美國公司的4,000名个人。商会的目的是通过一系列支持帮助美国公司在中国取得成功<ref name="About Us">{{Cite web|title=About Us|url=http://amchamchina.org/article/10|accessdate=2014-11-07|publisher=AmCham China|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141107102725/http://www.amchamchina.org/article/10|archivedate=2014-11-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。中国美国商会是唯一被[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]]官方认可的代表美国在華企业的商会<ref name="About Us" />。中国美国商会的总部设在[[北京市|北京市]]，並設有天津分会、华中分会（總部位於[[武汉市|武汉市]]）和东北分会（駐地位於[[沈阳市|沈阳市]]和[[大连市|大连市]]）。

第一家美国企業在華商会成立于1919年，创始成員共包括8家企业，其中就有[[标准石油|标准石油]]<ref name="Form Chamber in Peking">{{Cite web|title="Form Chamber in Peking, page 22"|url=http://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1919/08/27/issue.html|accessdate=2015-08-18|publisher=The New York Times|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215053239/https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1919/08/27/issue.html|archivedate=2020-12-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來该组织解散。1991年，中国美国商会作为一个無党派、非盈利的组织在[[中華人民共和國民政部|中華人民共和國民政部]]正式注册<ref name="AmCham China, Central China Chapter">{{Cite web|title=AmCham China, Central China Chapter|url=http://amchamchina.org/central_china_chapter/|accessdate=2014-11-07|publisher=AmCham China|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100220081856/http://www.amchamchina.org/central_china_chapter|archivedate=2010-02-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=《中外关系史辞典》|url=http://read.nongyekx.cn/gopreview?title=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%95%86%E4%BC%9A&ssid=10286087&dxid=000000349329&|accessdate=|author=朱杰勤，黄邦和主编 武汉：湖北人民出版社 1992 第488页|date=|format=|publisher=|language=}}</ref>。

2020年12月，中国美国商会在其年度答谢晚宴上宴请被[[美國對中華人民共和國的制裁|美国制裁]]的[[中国共产党|中国共产党]]党员[[王晨_(政治人物)|王晨]]，引发争议和批评<ref name="bbg">{{Cite web|title=China Sends Sanctioned Official to AmCham Dinner in Beijing|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-11/china-sends-sanctioned-official-to-amcham-dinner-in-beijing|accessdate=December 13, 2020|author=|date=December 10, 2020|agency=[[彭博新聞社|彭博新聞社]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212030516/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-11/china-sends-sanctioned-official-to-amcham-dinner-in-beijing|archivedate=2020-12-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="mccaul">{{Cite web|title=McCaul Statement on AmCham China Hosting Sanctioned CCP Official at Appreciation Gala - Committee on Foreign Affairs|url=https://gop-foreignaffairs.house.gov/press-release/mccaul-statement-on-amcham-china-hosting-sanctioned-ccp-official-at-appreciation-gala/|accessdate=13 December 2020|author=|date=11 December 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211231222/https://gop-foreignaffairs.house.gov/press-release/mccaul-statement-on-amcham-china-hosting-sanctioned-ccp-official-at-appreciation-gala/|archivedate=2020-12-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

